<!doctype html>
<html class="no-js" lang="">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Ability Score Generator</title>
  <meta name="description" content="">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.8.2/css/bulma.min.css" integrity="sha256-qS+snwBgqr+iFVpBB58C9UCxKFhyL03YHpZfdNUhSEw=" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
</head>

<body>
    <main class='section'>
        <div class='container'>
            <h1 class='title'>Ability Score Generator</h1>
            <hr>
            <p>Using the truly random number genarator from <a href="https://www.random.org">RANDOM.org</a> to generate truly random dice rolls for D&amp;D!</p>
            <h2>My Method - </h2>
            <div style='margin-left: 24px;'>
            <ol>
                <li>I query RANDOM.org for 24 random integers between 1 and 6 - emulating 24 seperate d6 dice rolls.</li>
                <li>I take the first four and add them up, then subtract the value of the lowest of the four. This is the first ability score.</li>
                <li>I them take the next four random integers, do the same process, and then so on until I have gone through all 24 integers.</li>
                <li>These six calculated numbers are then displayed below!</li>
            </ol>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <p>Hit the button and generate a new set of ability scores.</p>
            <p>You will then click below each score to determine which stat you want that score to be in.</p>

            <div style='margin-top: 10px;'>
                <button class="button" id="rollButton">Roll Some Abilities!</button>
            </div>


            <div class="columns">
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered is-size-3 scores" id='score1'>**</div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered is-size-3 scores" id='score2'>**</div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered is-size-3 scores" id='score3'>**</div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered is-size-3 scores" id='score4'>**</div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered is-size-3 scores" id='score5'>**</div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered is-size-3 scores" id='score6' style="margin-bottom: 24px;">**</div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns">
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
                    <div class="control" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat1" form='myForm' value='strength'>STR</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat1" form='myForm' value='dexterity'>DEX</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat1" form='myForm' value='constitution'>CON</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat1" form='myForm' value='intelligence'>INT</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat1" form='myForm' value='wisdom'>WIS</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat1" form='myForm' value='charisma'>CHA</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered strength stats" style="margin-bottom: 5px;" id="str2">
                    <div class="control" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat2" form='myForm' value='strength'>STR</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat2" form='myForm' value='dexterity'>DEX</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat2" form='myForm' value='constitution'>CON</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat2" form='myForm' value='intelligence'>INT</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat2" form='myForm' value='wisdom'>WIS</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat2" form='myForm' value='charisma'>CHA</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered strength stats" style="margin-bottom: 5px;" id="str3">
                    <div class="control" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat3" form='myForm' value='strength'>STR</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat3" form='myForm' value='dexterity'>DEX</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat3" form='myForm' value='constitution'>CON</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat3" form='myForm' value='intelligence'>INT</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat3" form='myForm' value='wisdom'>WIS</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat3" form='myForm' value='charisma'>CHA</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered strength stats" style="margin-bottom: 5px;" id="str4">
                    <div class="control" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat4" form='myForm' value='strength'>STR</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat4" form='myForm' value='dexterity'>DEX</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat4" form='myForm' value='constitution'>CON</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat4" form='myForm' value='intelligence'>INT</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat4" form='myForm' value='wisdom'>WIS</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat4" form='myForm' value='charisma'>CHA</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered strength stats" style="margin-bottom: 5px;" id="str5">
                    <div class="control" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat5" form='myForm' value='strength'>STR</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat5" form='myForm' value='dexterity'>DEX</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat5" form='myForm' value='constitution'>CON</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat5" form='myForm' value='intelligence'>INT</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat5" form='myForm' value='wisdom'>WIS</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat5" form='myForm' value='charisma'>CHA</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box column is-1 has-text-centered strength stats" style="margin-bottom: 5px;" id="str6">
                    <div class="control" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat6" form='myForm' value='strength'>STR</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat6" form='myForm' value='dexterity'>DEX</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat6" form='myForm' value='constitution'>CON</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat6" form='myForm' value='intelligence'>INT</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat6" form='myForm' value='wisdom'>WIS</label><br>
                        <label class="radio"><input type="radio" name="stat6" form='myForm' value='charisma'>CHA</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <br>
            <p>Type in a character name you want to save these stats for:</p>

            <div class="field">
                <div class="control">
                    <form action='/add-character' method="POST" id='myForm'>
                        <fieldset>
                            <input class="input is-primary" type="text" name="character">
                            <input type="submit" value="Save Character">
                            <input type="hidden" name="statNum1" value="" id="statNum1">
                            <input type="hidden" name="statNum2" value="" id="statNum2">
                            <input type="hidden" name="statNum3" value="" id="statNum3">
                            <input type="hidden" name="statNum4" value="" id="statNum4">
                            <input type="hidden" name="statNum5" value="" id="statNum5">
                            <input type="hidden" name="statNum6" value="" id="statNum6">
                        </fieldset>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <br>
            <p>Saved Characters:</p>
            <ul class="characters">
                {{#each characters}}
                    <li class='level' id='theCharList'>
                        <div class='level-left'>
                        <div class='savedName level-item'>{{this.charname}}:</div> 
                        <div class='saved level-item'>STR - {{this.strength}},</div> 
                        <div class='saved level-item'>DEX - {{this.dexterity}},</div>
                        <div class='saved level-item'>CON - {{this.constitution}},</div>
                        <div class='saved level-item'>INT - {{this.intelligence}},</div>
                        <div class='saved level-item'>WIS - {{this.wisdom}},</div>
                        <div class='saved level-item'>CHA - {{this.charisma}}</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>

        </div>
    </main>
 
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.js" integrity="sha256-WpOohJOqMqqyKL9FccASB9O0KwACQJpFTUBLTYOVvVU=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="random.js"></script>
    {{!-- <script src="statcontrol.js"></script> statcontrol is a work in progress--}}
</body>

</html>